abstract: Candy, stashed in the desk of Senator Patrick J. Toomey, Republican of Pennsylvania, is the only food allowed in the chamber.
lead_paragraph: Senator Cory Booker is a vegan. Senator Kamala Harris craves French fries. And then there’s Senator Ted Cruz, who once feasted on “machine gun bacon.”
keywords: Trump-Ukraine Whistle-blower Complaint and Impeachment Inquiry
